fwprop.note:
Start Action for Commands (11,22) to create one or more scheduling groups.
The command carries a list of group identifiers and their initial enable status.

fwprop.entryDesc:
Load the Group ID
in data pool verFailData

Run Command Verification
Failure Procedure to generate (1,4)
report with failure code VER_SCD_ILL_G

Set action outcome to 'failure'
with failure code VER_SCD_ST_FD

fwprop.note:
This procedure generates a (1,4) report for each group identifier which is already in
use or out-of-limits. The (1,4) reports are generated by the Command Verification
Failure Procedure. The start action is declared successful as long as there is at least
one group to be created.
